卡片加入手牌。","id":"ST15-004","img_full_url":"https://asia-hk.onepiece-cardgame.com/images/cardlist/card/ST15-004.png?260707","img_url":"../images/cardlist/card/ST15-004.png?260707","name":"薩吉","pack_id":"554015","power":2000,"rarity":"Common","trigger":null,"types":["白鬍子海賊團"]},{"attributes":["Special"],"block_number":3,"category":"Character","colors":["Red"],"cost":5,"counter":1000,"effect":"若自己的領航卡擁有包含『白鬍子海賊團』特徵時，這張角色卡獲得【速攻】。<br>(這張卡片在登場的回合即可攻擊)<br>【每回合1次】若這張角色卡因對手的效果即將離開場上時，可以替換成這張角色卡，在這個回合，力量值-2000。","id":"ST15-005","img_full_url":"https://asia-hk.onepiece-cardgame.com/images/cardlist/card/ST15-005.png?260707","img_url":"../images/cardlist/card/ST15-005.png?260707","name":"波特卡斯・D・艾斯","pack_id":"554015","power":6000,"rarity":"SuperRare","trigger":null,"types":["白鬍子海賊團"]}]